    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is application-specific functionality that belongs in ipythonqt. \n\nNow that the widget itself is stabilizing, it is probably worth building out some infrastructure for the application. Minimal though it is, the application will continue to accumulate functionality like this, and no doubt it will acquire a menu bar, tabs, a preferences dialog, etc over time. Currently, ipythonqt is a glorified frontend launch script (for which I am largely responsible). \n"
