    "body": "Increasing font size is a per-tab option, so resizing the window while increasing/decreasing size means other frontend wont match anymore.\n\nI can make the behavior append on all tabs at once and then (try to) implement something that keep nrow/ncol constant. \nWhat do you think the best solution/combinaison between\n- one/all tabs\n- keep windows size/ change windows size\n\nwe also will need to decide what to do when frontend migrate from one window another soon.\n"
